      "date": "2013-12-18 17:38:45.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nThis patch was created for testing purposes by request from Peter Jones.  The recent landing on b2_4 of the patch being reverted looks to be associated with new observed failures not seen previously on b2_4.  Creating a build of 2.4 tip with just the one patch removed to see if the problems are still seen.  This patch shouldn't land unless testing proves it improves the situation.",
