        "subject": "LU-3889 clio: revert LU-3433 for wrong cl_lock usage",
        "message": "LU-3889 clio: revert LU-3433 for wrong cl_lock usage\n\nRevert \"LU-3433 clio: wrong cl_lock usage\"\n\nThis reverts commit 1a04ba1a772659cc35f806210551ebf542c6365e.\n\nIt appears to be the direct cause of failures like LU-3889,\nnot seen in b2_4 before that commit.\n\nSigned-off-by: Bob Glossman <bob.glossman@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Idb5ff6c9ca6288d44d8eb46bb6d70d659efade0f\n"
      },
